<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">The Vietnam Veterans Against the War Web site has posted a <a href="http://www.vvaw.org/gallery/Bill_Davis.php" target="_blank">picture gallery in tribute of Bill</a>. Check here for plans for memorial meetings.
